+# PR-214 Remediation Report
+
+## Thread Classification
+
+- `T-214-01`: actionable
+- `T-214-02`: duplicate of `T-214-01`
+- `T-214-03`: obsolete
+- `T-214-04`: actionable
+- `T-214-05`: actionable
+
+## Changes Applied
+
+- `src/policy/approval_router.py`: normalize `approval_state` before calling `build_preview_payload`, so `manual_review` is consistently converted to `human_review_required`.
+- `src/policy/preview.py`: preserve `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` in the fallback `preview_unavailable` payload.
+- `tests/test_preview.py`: added fallback regression coverage for `preview_enabled=false` with `manual_review` input, and strengthened the existing fallback assertions.
+- `docs/approval_policy.md`: corrected the documented fallback payload and note text to match the repaired behavior.
+
+## Intentionally Not Applied
+
+- `T-214-02`: duplicate thread; handled by the `T-214-01` fix.
+- `T-214-03`: outdated suggestion to revive legacy preview behavior; not applied.
+
+## Verification
+
+- Targeted unit tests to run: `python -m unittest tests.test_preview tests.test_approval_router`
